    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera is a driver-focused example featuring the M96 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, paired to a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. The drivetrain remains robust, providing excellent throttle response and a linear power band. Chassis dynamics are sharp, utilizing its MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension to maximize mechanical grip. Recent service ensures the cooling system and Brembo braking hardware are in peak operating condition. A mechanically honest machine for the purist seeking the quintessential rear-engine, rear-wheel-drive experience.",
