      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained 2017 Porsche Macan S finished in sophisticated Volcano Grey Metallic. This vehicle strikes the perfect balance for a discerning driver who values both sports-car performance and everyday utility. The exterior maintains a deep, mirror-like gloss, showing only the minor, inevitable stone chips on the front fascia consistent with careful highway use. The 19-inch Macan Design wheels are free of curb rash and are wrapped in premium tires with significant tread remaining. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of German craftsmanship; the black leather interior is supple and well-preserved, featuring 14-way power-adjustable heated seats and a panoramic sunroof that opens up the cabin beautifully. Every feature, from the responsive PCM navigation system to the crisp Bose Surround Sound, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this Macan S is robust, benefiting from a documented service history at authorized centers. It has recently undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection and fresh oil service, ensuring the 3.0L V6 twin-turbo engine and PDK transmission deliver the seamless, punchy acceleration the model is known for. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that has been kept in a climate-controlled garage, offering a turn-key experience for its next owner.",
